message.text:
📣 APPLICATION PERIOD EXTENDED‼️⏳

Hindi pa ba kumpleto ang requirements mo o hindi ka pa nakakapagpasa ng application? Worry no more—dahil may good news kami para sa’yo! 

Extended na ang ating application period! May dagdag na oras ka na para ayusin, tapusin, at siguraduhing maipasa ang lahat ng iyong kailangan. 📑

Huwag nang hintayin ang huling araw—gamitin ang mga oras na ito para makumpleto ang iyong application at maging bahagi ng kwentong bubuuin natin ngayong taon.

Kilalanin pa ang FEU IABF Student Council S.Y. 2025–2026 divisions dito: https://bit.ly/IABF_SC_Division_Description_and_Requirements

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
📣 APPLICATION PERIOD EXTENDED‼️⏳

Hindi pa ba kumpleto ang requirements mo o hindi ka pa nakakapagpasa ng application? Worry no more—dahil may good news kami para sa’yo! 

Extended na ang ating application period! May dagdag na oras ka na para ayusin, tapusin, at siguraduhing maipasa ang lahat ng iyong kailangan. 📑

Huwag nang hintayin ang huling araw—gamitin ang mga oras na ito para makumpleto ang iyong application at maging bahagi ng kwentong bubuuin natin ngayong taon.

Kilalanin pa ang FEU IABF Student Council S.Y. 2025–2026 divisions dito: https://bit.ly/IABF_SC_Division_Description_and_Requirements

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗺: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗺: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗺: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

#TamHunt2025 
#MembershipApplications2025
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers
